28
00:05:13,397 --> 00:05:14,654
I'll replace one for you.

29
00:05:18,569 --> 00:05:21,398
But the time is correct.

30
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:33,000
(Episode 2: The Most Familiar Stranger)

31
00:05:41,050 --> 00:05:42,284
Shi Wen.

32
00:05:43,170 --> 00:05:44,393
Shi Wen.

33
00:05:44,970 --> 00:05:46,503
I had a nightmare.

34
00:05:47,417 --> 00:05:49,486
I thought I'd never see you again.

35
00:05:52,930 --> 00:05:55,877
You... Who are you? Do I know you?

36
00:05:56,449 --> 00:05:59,721
Shi Wen, it's me! Don't you remember me?

37
00:06:02,209 --> 00:06:03,304
I'm sorry.

38
00:06:03,329 --> 00:06:05,315
We get so many customers here,

39
00:06:05,410 --> 00:06:06,825
I must have forgotten you.

40
00:06:06,850 --> 00:06:09,276
I'm not just a customer. I'm Shen Nan!

41
00:06:09,329 --> 00:06:10,893
Earlier, I was still...

42
