It's always been a still-life sketch.

44
00:06:21,970 --> 00:06:24,573
Brother, are you okay?

45
00:06:24,610 --> 00:06:28,065
Should I call a doctor for you?

46
00:06:35,359 --> 00:06:38,202
(Wednesday, June 5th at 5:12 p.m.)

47
00:06:39,786 --> 00:06:42,327
Time has returned to three months ago.

48
00:06:46,689 --> 00:06:48,398
Has time reset itself?

49
00:06:57,722 --> 00:06:59,140
Is he crazy?

50
