Jiang Yilin.

52
00:07:05,889 --> 00:07:07,116
Jiang Yilin.

53
00:07:08,930 --> 00:07:10,960
Hello, scan the QR code to order.

54
00:07:11,401 --> 00:07:13,272
Yilin, it's me!

55
00:07:14,290 --> 00:07:15,679
Why act so familiar?

56
00:07:16,050 --> 00:07:17,929
Who are you? I don't know you.

57
00:07:18,449 --> 00:07:20,327
It's me, Shen Nan.

58
00:07:21,410 --> 00:07:22,781
What Shen Nan?

59
00:07:23,329 --> 00:07:25,063
Let me tell you, eating is fine,

60
00:07:25,079 --> 00:07:27,008
but harassing the owner?

61
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:28,446
I'll beat you so hard you wouldn't

62
00:07:28,471 --> 00:07:29,852
be able to find your home.

63
00:07:30,677 --> 00:07:32,608
Why doesn't anyone remember me?

64
00:07:33,115 --> 00:07:34,398
Never mind.

65
00:07:34,991 --> 00:07:36,732
Just get me fried rice.

66
00:07:36,970 --> 00:07:39,499
Oh, and add two eggs.

67
00:07:40,209 --> 00:07:41,427
One order of egg fried rice

68
00:07:41,435 --> 00:07:42,555
with two eggs.

69
00:07:46,046 --> 00:07:47,744
Hey, how did you know?

70
00:07:47,769 --> 00:07:48,956
Of course, I know.

71
00:07:48,972 --> 00:07:50,331
You can't bear to drink it,

72
00:07:50,339 --> 00:07:51,530
so I'll drink it for you.

73
00:07:51,554 --> 00:07:53,145
Oh, you peeping maniac!

74
00:07:53,170 --> 00:07:54,569
Daring to spy on me? Get out!

75
00:07:54,594 --> 00:07:56,015
Let me explain!

76
00:07:56,081 --> 00:07:58,882
Fine, fine, I'll leave. Still not okay?

77
00:07:59,050 --> 00:08:00,804
Don't let me see you again!

78
00:08:03,940 --> 00:08:05,327
Crazy person.

79
00:08:24,891 --> 00:08:26,544
Who are you?

80
00:08:26,898 --> 00:08:28,308
You don't need to know.

81
00:08:28,649 --> 00:08:30,453
The quantum necklace brought you back

82
00:08:30,477 --> 00:08:31,977
to three months ago.

83
00:08:32,689 --> 00:08:34,075
Time has been reset.

84
00:08:34,530 --> 00:08:36,272
Everything you interact with

85
00:08:36,288 --> 00:08:38,154
will change because of this.

86
00:08:38,689 --> 00:08:40,170
The butterfly effect will lead

87
00:08:40,195 --> 00:08:41,987
to unimaginable consequences.

88
00:08:42,026 --> 00:08:43,200
What consequences?

89
00:08:44,609 --> 00:08:45,880
You don't need to know.

90
00:08:46,731 --> 00:08:48,723
If you forcefully alter the ending...

91
00:08:49,170 --> 00:08:50,209
Otherwise...

92
00:08:50,770 --> 00:08:51,903
Otherwise what?

93
00:08:53,969 --> 00:08:55,700
Say it! Otherwise what? Tell me!

94
00:08:58,369 --> 00:09:00,442
You stop talking at the crucial moment?

95
00:09:05,489 --> 00:09:06,622
It's fine.

96
00:09:08,250 --> 00:09:09,343
Then let's start over and

97
00:09:09,359 --> 00:09:10,875
get to know each other again.

98
00:09:59,729 --> 00:10:02,098
Let the rain fall completely.

99
00:10:02,130 --> 00:10:03,488
You two, slow down!

100
00:10:03,513 --> 00:10:04,796
Shi Wen, that note you sang was off-key.

101
00:10:04,820 --> 00:10:06,106
Brother, did you hear it?

102
00:10:06,130 --> 00:10:07,741
So, that guy from this morning

103
00:10:07,765 --> 00:10:09,554
wasn't a local from our town?

104
00:10:09,785 --> 00:10:11,296
Definitely not. Are there people in

105
00:10:11,304 --> 00:10:12,626
this town that I don't know?

106
00:10:12,650 --> 00:10:14,074
What if he's a tourist?

107
00:10:14,190 --> 00:10:16,528
Who cares who he is? Whatever.

108
00:10:17,472 --> 00:10:18,653
Hey, hey!

109
00:10:19,626 --> 00:10:20,723
Who's that?

110
00:10:20,748 --> 00:10:21,762
- Hmm?
- Hmm?

111
00:10:22,369 --> 00:10:24,387
I think I heard something inside.

112
00:10:25,209 --> 00:10:26,625
Could it be a thief?

113
00:10:26,650 --> 00:10:28,029
Impossible. I locked the door

114
00:10:28,053 --> 00:10:28,951
when I left.

115
00:10:38,290 --> 00:10:41,153
Three, two, one...

116
00:10:41,290 --> 00:10:43,153
- Come out!
- Come out!

117
00:10:43,278 --> 00:10:45,185
Come out! Come out!

118
00:10:45,209 --> 00:10:46,379
- Get the thief!
- Come out!

119
00:10:46,404 --> 00:10:49,209
Don't hit me! It's me, it's me, it's me!

120
00:10:50,250 --> 00:10:51,340
Put it down.

121
00:10:51,436 --> 00:10:52,717
Calm down, calm down!

122
00:10:54,546 --> 00:10:55,905
It's raining outside.

123
00:10:55,930 --> 00:10:57,707
I just needed a place to take shelter.

124
00:10:58,202 --> 00:10:59,625
I saw Shi Wen wasn't here,

125
00:10:59,650 --> 00:11:00,781
so I had no choice but

126
00:11:00,789 --> 00:11:01,812
to come in myself.

127
00:11:02,875 --> 00:11:05,168
Then how do you have the key to my café?

128
00:11:06,569 --> 00:11:08,467
I accidentally picked it up.

129
00:11:08,491 --> 00:11:10,171
Here, I'll give it back.

130
00:11:11,025 --> 00:11:12,178
Don't trust him, brother.

131
00:11:12,194 --> 00:11:13,808
Shi Wen, we should call the police.

132
00:11:13,832 --> 00:11:15,722
- Hey.
- Who are you, really?

133
00:11:15,890 --> 00:11:16,913
If you don't tell us,

134
00:11:16,938 --> 00:11:17,950
I'll call the police for real.

135
00:11:17,988 --> 00:11:19,395
Put that down first.

136
00:11:19,449 --> 00:11:21,010
Okay, okay, I'll explain.

137
00:11:23,290 --> 00:11:26,371
Actually... I lost my job.

138
00:11:27,449 --> 00:11:29,225
I wanted to work at the café.

139
00:11:29,250 --> 00:11:31,505
I just need a temporary place to stay.

140
00:11:31,530 --> 00:11:32,738
Work?

141
00:11:32,819 --> 00:11:34,233
You came in the middle of the night

142
00:11:34,249 --> 00:11:35,931
looking for a job? Don't believe him!

143
00:11:35,955 --> 00:11:37,340
I swear, I'm not a bad person.

144
00:11:38,018 --> 00:11:40,410
I can leave my ID with you.

145
00:11:42,203 --> 00:11:43,425
Shen Nan.

146
00:11:51,911 --> 00:11:53,434
Come.

147
00:11:54,561 --> 00:11:56,035
Can we trust him?

148
00:11:56,130 --> 00:11:57,145
I'm not a scammer,

149
00:11:57,153 --> 00:11:58,144
you have to believe me!

150
00:11:58,168 --> 00:11:59,246
Shut up.

151
00:11:59,530 --> 00:12:01,169
My mom isn't here, and I can't

152
00:12:01,177 --> 00:12:02,857
manage everything alone.

153
00:12:03,089 --> 00:12:05,074
Free labor, no pay needed.

154
00:12:05,410 --> 00:12:07,918
Seems like there's no reason to say no.

155
00:12:08,418 --> 00:12:11,356
Plus, he does look kind of pitiful.

156
00:12:12,410 --> 00:12:13,441
- Hey.
- Hey.

157
00:12:13,969 --> 00:12:15,387
You can stay here,

158
00:12:15,729 --> 00:12:18,340
but we'll hold onto your ID.

159
00:12:35,547 --> 00:12:37,817
Who is it? What are you doing?

160
00:12:39,060 --> 00:12:40,544
I came to get face wash.

161
00:12:40,569 --> 00:12:43,278
How do you know where I keep my stuff?

162
00:12:44,050 --> 00:12:45,268
I accidentally saw it yesterday

163
00:12:45,277 --> 00:12:46,246
when I used the bathroom.

164
00:12:46,271 --> 00:12:47,934
Then remember to knock next time.

165
00:12:52,794 --> 00:12:54,479
I never needed to knock before.

166
00:12:55,171 --> 00:12:56,877
Do I need to knock now?

167
00:12:57,929 --> 00:12:59,057
Before?

168
00:13:03,979 --> 00:13:05,119
Nothing. I'll grab your

169
00:13:05,127 --> 00:13:06,175
toothpaste for you.

170
00:13:06,199 --> 00:13:09,057
No need! Get out, out, out!

171
00:13:21,688 --> 00:13:25,372
Oh my God, didn't he love neat and tidy?

172
00:13:26,209 --> 00:13:27,609
It's such a mess.

173
00:13:37,770 --> 00:13:39,288
It's everywhere.

174
00:14:01,562 --> 00:14:02,562
Hey!

175
00:14:02,569 --> 00:14:03,718
Why are you randomly entering

176
00:14:03,743 --> 00:14:05,044
my room and touching my things?

177
00:14:05,069 --> 00:14:06,218
Your room is so messy.

178
00:14:06,242 --> 00:14:08,002
I was just trying to help you clean up!

179
00:14:08,026 --> 00:14:10,184
I don't like strangers in my room.

180
00:14:10,209 --> 00:14:11,608
From now on, just focus on

181
00:14:11,632 --> 00:14:13,101
the downstairs café and guesthouse.

182
00:14:13,290 --> 00:14:14,718
Don't do anything else.

183
00:14:15,209 --> 00:14:17,170
Put that down and leave.

184
00:14:36,849 --> 00:14:38,096
Watch carefully.

185
00:14:38,226 --> 00:14:40,903
First, pour the milk into the coffee.

186
00:14:40,928 --> 00:14:42,608
Let it flow like this.

187
00:14:43,290 --> 00:14:47,303
Then mix it to about 50–60%.

188
00:14:47,369 --> 00:14:49,454
Continue pouring from the center

189
00:14:49,479 --> 00:14:51,728
outwards towards the two edges.

190
00:14:52,209 --> 00:14:55,320
Finally, lift and finish it.

191
00:14:55,650 --> 00:14:56,939
And like this,

192
00:14:56,955 --> 00:14:58,822
you get a basic heart shape.

193
00:14:59,650 --> 00:15:02,101
Got it? Give it a try.

194
00:15:03,849 --> 00:15:05,374
Let me try.

195
00:15:21,451 --> 00:15:22,983
Not bad!

196
00:15:23,130 --> 00:15:24,803
You've got some talent.

197
00:15:24,962 --> 00:15:26,459
Someone taught me before.

198
00:15:26,891 --> 00:15:28,584
He was a great teacher.

199
00:15:30,849 --> 00:15:32,329
Then let me teach you to make desserts.

200
00:15:32,354 --> 00:15:33,642
I already know desserts.

201
00:15:33,667 --> 00:15:35,181
I can even make tiramisu.

202
00:15:37,010 --> 00:15:39,587
Aren't these menu from my café?

203
00:15:46,689 --> 00:15:48,298
It's pretty good, huh?

204
00:15:48,323 --> 00:15:49,886
Not bad at all.

205
00:15:50,018 --> 00:15:51,120
Of course.

206
00:15:51,170 --> 00:15:52,565
Hiring me, you've really

207
00:15:52,581 --> 00:15:54,261
found yourself a gem.

208
00:15:55,096 --> 00:15:56,307
It's alright.

209
00:15:56,530 --> 00:15:57,623
Perfect.

210
00:15:57,648 --> 00:15:59,655
I'll leave the café to you today.

211
00:15:59,686 --> 00:16:01,252
- I'm taking a day off.
- Mm.

212
00:16:01,369 --> 00:16:03,104
- You two, come with me to paint.
- Mm.

213
00:16:07,250 --> 00:16:09,047
Do you think he's reliable?

214
00:16:09,410 --> 00:16:10,917
Don't worry. He seems to

215
00:16:10,933 --> 00:16:12,683
treat Shi Wen quite well.

216
00:16:13,258 --> 00:16:14,688
Let's go paint, big brother!

217
00:16:14,810 --> 00:16:16,422
Come on. Let's go.

218
00:16:30,226 --> 00:16:31,855
Isn't this me?

219
00:16:32,410 --> 00:16:34,316
Why does he have a portrait of me?

220
00:16:35,849 --> 00:16:38,176
He shouldn't have known me back then.

221
00:16:41,130 --> 00:16:42,851
Could he have remembered me?

222
00:17:05,169 --> 00:17:06,288
Shi Wen.

223
00:17:07,889 --> 00:17:08,904
This is a portrait

224
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:09,987
you drew of me, isn't it?

225
00:17:10,012 --> 00:17:12,053
Do you remember when you drew it?

226
00:17:12,609 --> 00:17:14,344
It really does look exactly like you.

227
00:17:14,369 --> 00:17:16,985
But I don't recall ever drawing you.

228
00:17:17,010 --> 00:17:18,017
Think harder.

229
00:17:18,041 --> 00:17:19,275
Is there any trace of me

230
00:17:19,300 --> 00:17:20,314
in your memories?

231
00:17:22,095 --> 00:17:23,544
In my memories...

232
00:17:23,569 --> 00:17:25,381
Should there be traces of you?

233
00:17:30,810 --> 00:17:32,131
Of course not.

234
00:17:33,250 --> 00:17:35,124
We didn't know each other before.

235
00:17:37,103 --> 00:17:38,454
This drawing clearly was

236
00:17:38,479 --> 00:17:40,159
drawn before we met.

237
00:17:40,577 --> 00:17:41,577
Could it be...

238
00:17:43,129 --> 00:17:44,526
Could it be...

239
00:17:44,854 --> 00:17:47,077
that he had memories of me,

240
00:17:47,530 --> 00:17:49,335
but temporarily forgot them?

241
00:18:04,577 --> 00:18:06,397
No need to examine it that closely.

242
00:18:06,422 --> 00:18:08,092
It's obvious that this is me.

243
00:18:08,136 --> 00:18:10,209
Huh? No. Look here,

244
00:18:10,258 --> 00:18:11,425
this part is different.

245
00:18:11,450 --> 00:18:14,155
Your Adam's apple is bigger.

246
00:18:14,409 --> 00:18:15,436
Exactly.

247
00:18:15,530 --> 00:18:16,799
Look, you've got crow's feet

248
00:18:16,823 --> 00:18:17,998
around your eyes.

249
00:18:18,022 --> 00:18:19,452
But the drawing doesn't.

250
00:18:19,477 --> 00:18:20,505
Forget it.

251
00:18:20,530 --> 00:18:22,225
With you two siblings in this world...

252
00:18:22,250 --> 00:18:25,038
nothing strange seems impossible.

253
00:18:25,288 --> 00:18:27,608
Shi Wen will stop drawing.

254
00:18:27,730 --> 00:18:29,776
Maybe he just drew it casually before.

255
00:18:29,801 --> 00:18:31,420
It just happens to resemble you.

256
00:18:31,474 --> 00:18:32,866
Why would he stop drawing?

257
00:18:33,050 --> 00:18:35,144
He said he doesn't like drawing.

258
00:18:35,169 --> 00:18:36,526
He only paints sometimes

259
00:18:36,542 --> 00:18:37,902
to pass the time.

260
00:18:38,210 --> 00:18:39,710
Boss! Boss!

261
00:18:39,970 --> 00:18:41,585
There's a customer. Let me handle it.

262
00:18:44,001 --> 00:18:46,798
No, his dream is to paint.

263
00:18:48,649 --> 00:18:49,940
- Jiang Yilin.
- Hmm?

264
00:18:50,010 --> 00:18:51,525
Do me a favor. There's a big

265
00:18:51,533 --> 00:18:53,105
drawing competition in the city.

266
00:18:53,129 --> 00:18:54,945
The registration deadline has passed.

267
00:18:54,970 --> 00:18:56,563
I heard you know someone

268
00:18:56,572 --> 00:18:58,009
on the organizing team.

269
00:18:58,409 --> 00:19:00,440
Help me get a competition pass.

270
00:19:00,530 --> 00:19:01,745
Why should I help you?

271
00:19:01,770 --> 00:19:02,863
You're not helping me.

272
00:19:02,895 --> 00:19:04,026
You're helping Shi Wen.

273
00:19:04,050 --> 00:19:05,121
Don't you want to help him

274
00:19:05,137 --> 00:19:06,104
achieve his dream?

275
00:19:06,129 --> 00:19:07,512
I say, as an employee,

276
00:19:07,537 --> 00:19:09,937
you're being way too nice to Shi Wen.

277
00:19:10,124 --> 00:19:11,320
Do you have ulterior motives?

278
00:19:11,345 --> 00:19:12,948
- Are you helping or not?
- Nope.

279
00:19:20,450 --> 00:19:21,581
You've got a mole on

280
00:19:21,589 --> 00:19:22,553
the left side of your butt.

281
00:19:22,578 --> 00:19:25,104
Your WeChat payment password is 666888.

282
00:19:25,129 --> 00:19:26,394
You've got a crush on three

283
00:19:26,418 --> 00:19:27,702
