00:39:38,770 --> 00:39:39,904
- Shen Nan,
- Huh?

573
00:39:39,929 --> 00:39:41,840
Who gives something away
and then takes it back?

574
00:39:41,865 --> 00:39:42,889
Give it to me quickly.

575
00:39:42,906 --> 00:39:44,586
Shen Nan, give it to me.

576
00:39:44,969 --> 00:39:46,009
Give it to me.

577
00:39:47,531 --> 00:39:49,334
- You guys,
- Give it to me!

578
00:39:51,650 --> 00:39:53,306
Is something wrong?

579
00:39:53,961 --> 00:39:55,094
The coffee's here.

580
00:39:55,102 --> 00:39:56,786
You guys go check the stuff.

581
00:39:56,810 --> 00:39:57,978
I'll go.

582
00:40:14,090 --> 00:40:15,314
Shi Wen,

583
00:40:16,228 --> 00:40:17,457
your painting is getting

584
00:40:17,481 --> 00:40:18,782
better and better.

585
00:40:18,806 --> 00:40:20,197
Wow, Shi Wen,

586
00:40:20,353 --> 00:40:22,145
I didn't expect you to improve so much.

587
00:40:22,287 --> 00:40:23,638
So many years,

588
00:40:23,663 --> 00:40:25,038
when did you secretly practice?

589
00:40:25,062 --> 00:40:27,065
Brother, it's just you don't know this,

590
00:40:27,090 --> 00:40:28,636
Shi Wen's sketches

591
00:40:28,661 --> 00:40:30,528
were often copied by others.

592
00:40:30,610 --> 00:40:31,871
Looks like we're going to

593
00:40:31,879 --> 00:40:33,218
be friends with a great artist.

594
00:40:33,242 --> 00:40:35,785
- Mm.
- Next time when you eat, it's free.

595
00:40:35,810 --> 00:40:37,386
Next time at the restaurant,

596
00:40:37,395 --> 00:40:38,945
I'll take lots of pictures.

597
00:40:38,969 --> 00:40:41,303
Maybe later you'll have fans coming.

598
00:40:41,329 --> 00:40:43,943
Then my restaurant will be a hit.

599
00:40:44,329 --> 00:40:46,623
Brother, don't flatter me.

600
00:40:46,730 --> 00:40:48,705
There are many people better than me.

601
00:40:48,730 --> 00:40:50,105
If you're really my friend,

602
00:40:50,130 --> 00:40:51,653
next time I come to your restaurant,

603
00:40:51,669 --> 00:40:53,036
give me a discount.

604
00:40:53,310 --> 00:40:54,409
Shen Nan.

605
00:40:54,529 --> 00:40:56,232
Then take good care

606
00:40:56,263 --> 00:40:57,997
of our Shi Wen from now on.

607
00:40:58,049 --> 00:40:59,570
Let's go, let's go eat.

608
00:40:59,604 --> 00:41:01,730
- Let's go.
- I'm not going for the meal.

609
00:41:02,130 --> 00:41:04,232
I have a competition in a week.

610
00:41:04,257 --> 00:41:05,974
I want to practice more.

611
00:41:10,179 --> 00:41:13,287
