(Wang Haoran. Gu Shi Wen. Liu Shiya)

614
00:41:24,889 --> 00:41:26,290
Gu Shi Wen.

615
00:41:32,009 --> 00:41:34,821
Shi Wen, your painting was selected!

616
00:41:35,250 --> 00:41:36,500
That's great! I thought

617
00:41:36,508 --> 00:41:38,188
I wouldn't be selected.

618
00:41:38,492 --> 00:41:39,437
When I get back,

619
00:41:39,445 --> 00:41:40,500
I'll celebrate with you.

620
00:41:40,524 --> 00:41:42,449
- Oh, Shi Wen.
- Shi Wen.

621
00:41:42,770 --> 00:41:44,117
Isn't that the colorblind guy

622
00:41:44,133 --> 00:41:45,186
from our class?

623
00:41:45,210 --> 00:41:47,297
- He actually got selected?
- He got selected.

624
00:41:48,250 --> 00:41:49,257
His skill is terrible

625
00:41:49,266 --> 00:41:51,023
and he calls himself an artist.

626
00:41:51,766 --> 00:41:53,593
- With this little skill?
- With this skill,

627
00:41:53,618 --> 00:41:54,625
he dares to enter a competition?

628
00:41:54,650 --> 00:41:56,423
- Exactly.
- Yeah, isn't he afraid people

629
00:41:56,439 --> 00:41:57,915
will know he's colorblind?

630
00:42:00,204 --> 00:42:01,204
Hey.

631
00:42:02,610 --> 00:42:04,719
Looks like you three

632
00:42:05,009 --> 00:42:07,009
bullied Shi Wen before, huh?

633
00:42:07,049 --> 00:42:08,297
Who are you?

634
00:42:08,650 --> 00:42:10,688
What's it to you? Get lost.

635
00:42:10,730 --> 00:42:13,039
Kid, you want to die?

636
00:42:13,290 --> 00:42:15,703
Daring to cause trouble on our turf?

637
00:42:17,529 --> 00:42:20,828
Gu Shi Wen's matter is my matter.

638
00:43:21,811 --> 00:43:23,811
(Next episode)

639
00:43:24,810 --> 00:43:26,490
What happened?

640
00:43:29,489 --> 00:43:30,975
Nothing much.

641
00:43:31,009 --> 00:43:32,030
Shen Nan,

642
00:43:32,055 --> 00:43:33,649
why does the wound on

643
00:43:33,657 --> 00:43:35,524
your face and my brother's...

644
00:43:37,831 --> 00:43:40,042
- Umm... A cat scratched me.
- Umm... I got into a fight.

645
00:43:43,329 --> 00:43:44,606
Slow down.

646
00:43:44,730 --> 00:43:46,528
I'm not drunk, I can walk.

647
00:43:49,849 --> 00:43:51,505
Jiang Yilin can't drink either.

648
00:43:51,537 --> 00:43:53,025
He said he'd beat me.

649
00:43:53,049 --> 00:43:54,944
Yeah, yeah, you're the best at drinking.

650
00:43:54,969 --> 00:43:57,344
Shi Wen, the great artist, is the best.

651
00:43:57,369 --> 00:43:58,464
Slow down, slow down.

652
00:43:58,489 --> 00:44:00,362
- You'll fall.
- I'm not drunk, I can walk.

653
00:44:01,242 --> 00:44:02,521
Be careful.
